     |-- shared_types_test.go\n|   |           |-- zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n|   |-- common/\n|   |   |-- types/\n|   |       |-- types.go\n|   |-- router/\n|   |   |-- backend.go\n|   |   |-- config.go\n|   |   |-- config_test.go\n|   |   |-- errors.go\n|   |   |-- health.go\n|   |   |-- informer.go\n|   |   |-- jwt.go\n|   |   |-- jwt_test.go\n|   |   |-- loadbalancer.go\n|   |   |-- middleware.go\n|   |   |-- middleware_test.go\n|   |   |-- proxy.go\n|   |   |-- router.go\n|   |   |-- server.go\n|   |   |-- server_test.go\n|   |   |-- session_manager.go\n|   |-- store/\n|   |   |-- codec.go\n|   |   |-- codec_test.go\n|   |   |-- singleton.go\n|   |   |-- singleton_test.go\n|   |   |-- store.go\n|   |   |-- store_redis.go\n|   |   |-- store_redis_test.go\n|   |   |-- store_valkey.go\n|   |   |-- store_valkey_test.go\n|   |-- workloadmanager/\n|       |-- handler/\n|       |   |-- constants.go\n|       |   |-- models.go\n|       |   |-- sandbox_create.go\n|       |   |-- sandbox_delete.go\n|       |   |-- sandbox_delete_test.go\n|       |   |-- sandbox_lifecycle.go\n|       |   |-- sandbox_lifecycle_test.go\n|       |-- reconciler/\n|       |   |-- agentruntime.go\n|       |   |-- codeinterpreter.go\n|       |   |-- event_handlers.go\n|       |   |-- metrics.go\n|       |   |-- metrics_test.go\n|       |   |-- pod.go\n|       |   |-- reconciler.go\n|       |   |-- sync.go\n|       |   |-- types.go\n|       |-- response/\n|           |-- response.go\n|           |-- response_test.go\n|-- project.md\n|-- proposal.md\n|-- python-sdk/\n|   |-- design.md\n|   |-- spec.md\n|-- sandbox-orchestration/\n|   |-- design.md\n|   |-- spec.md\n|-- session-routing/\n|   |-- design.md\n|   |-- spec.md\n|-- session-store/\n|   |-- design.md\n|   |-- spec.md\n|-- test_spec.md\n|-- testing/\n    |-- agentcube_tdd_manifest.md\n```\n\n---\n\n## 2. DESIGN / SPEC / STAGE DOCUMENTS\n\n### Root-level design documents:\n- **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md`** -- AR-012: Session Store Interface Definition (687 lines). Defines the Store interface, both Redis and Valkey implementations, singleton pattern, data structures, API contracts, testing strategy, and deployment considerations.\n- **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md`** -- AR-014: Valkey Storage Implementation Delta Spec (269 lines). GIVEN/WHEN/THEN acceptance scenarios for Valkey backend.\n- **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`** -- AR-011: Router JWT authentication (this is from a previous AR, not the current one).\n- **`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/project.md`** -- AgentCube OpenSpec Project Context (45 lines). High-level architecture, tech stack, conventions.\n\n### Spec domain directories:\n- **`session-store/spec.md`** (118 lines) -- Session Store Specification with GIVEN/WHEN/THEN scenarios\n- **`session-store/design.md`** (206 lines) -- Session Store design with exact interface signatures, struct definitions, environment variables, and operation summaries\n- **`deployment/client-go.md`** -- Kubernetes client code spec for `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- **`sandbox-orchestration/design.md`**, **`sandbox-orchestration/spec.md`**\n- **`ci-cd/design.md`**, **`ci-cd/spec.md`**\n- **`code-execution/design.md`**, **`code-execution/spec.md`**\n- **`session-routing/design.md`**, **`session-routing/spec.md`**\n- **`idle-cleanup/design.md`**, **`idle-cleanup/spec.md`**\n- **`python-sdk/design.md`**, **`python-sdk/spec.md`**\n- **`cli-toolkit/design.md`**, **`cli-toolkit/spec.md`**\n- **`integrations/design.md`**, **`integrations/spec.md`**\n- **`deployment/design.md`**, **`deployment/spec.md`**\n\n### AR change folders (AR-001 through AR-014):\nEach contains some combination of `proposal.md`, `design.md`, `delta-spec.md`, and `tasks.md`. The most relevant to the store module are:\n- **AR-012** -- Session Store Interface Definition\n- **AR-013** -- Redis Storage Implementation\n- **AR-014** -- Valkey Storage Implementation\n\n---\n\n## 3. GO MODULE STRUCTURE\n\n**`go.mod`** (full contents):\n```\nmodule github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube\n\ngo 1.25.0\n\nrequire (\n    github.com/alicebob/miniredis/v2 v2.37.0\n    github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0\n    github.com/golang-jwt/jwt/v5 v5.2.1\n    github.com/google/uuid v1.6.0\n    github.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.22.0\n    github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.18.0\n    github.com/stretchr/testify v1.11.1\n    github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go v1.0.73\n    golang.org/x/net v0.51.0\n    k8s.io/api v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1\n    k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1\n    sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2\n)\n```\n\n**Package structure:**\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store` -- Session store (Redis + Valkey)\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/router` -- HTTP router/proxy with JWT auth\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types` -- Type aliases (SandboxInfo, EntryPoint)\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` -- K8s CRD types (AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter)\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/handler` -- Sandbox lifecycle management\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler` -- K8s reconciler controller\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/response` -- HTTP response helpers\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset` -- Generated K8s clientset\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers` -- Shared informer factory\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/listers` -- Lister interfaces\n\n---\n\n## 4. EXISTING STORE IMPLEMENTATIONS AND INTERFACES\n\n### Store Interface (`pkg/store/store.go`):\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *types.SandboxInfo) error\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListSandboxes(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n    ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n    Close() error\n}\n```\n\n### Redis Implementation (`pkg/store/store_redis.go`, 274 lines):\n- Uses `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n- Full implementation of all 10 Store interface methods\n- Uses Pipeline for atomic multi-command operations (SETNX + ZADD x2)\n- Uses MGET for batch loading in `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs`\n- Environment variables: `REDIS_ADDR`, `REDIS_PASSWORD`, `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`\n\n### Valkey Implementation (`pkg/store/store_valkey.go`, 253 lines):\n- Uses `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n- Full implementation of all 10 Store interface methods\n- Uses `DoMulti` for atomic multi-command operations\n- Uses individual `GetSandbox` calls per session ID in List methods (NOT MGET -- this differs from the design doc)\n- Environment variables: `VALKEY_ADDR`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD`, `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED`, `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE`, `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE`\n\n### Singleton (`pkg/store/singleton.go`):\n- `Storage()` returns singleton via `sync.Once`\n- Provider selection via `STORE_TYPE` env var (default: `redis`, supports `valkey`)\n\n### Codec (`pkg/store/codec.go`):\n- `encodeSandboxInfo()` / `decodeSandboxInfo()` -- JSON marshal/unmarshal helpers\n\n### Test files:\n- `store_redis_test.go` (583 lines) -- Comprehensive integration tests using `miniredis`\n- `store_valkey_test.go` (237 lines) -- Validation-only tests (no live Valkey mock)\n- `singleton_test.go` (85 lines) -- Provider selection and concurrency tests\n- `codec_test.go` (111 lines) -- Encode/decode round-trip tests\n\n### SandboxInfo type (`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go`):\n```go\ntype SandboxInfo struct {\n    SessionID      string       `json:\"sessionId\"`\n    SandboxName    string       `json:\"sandboxName\"`\n    SandboxID      string       `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n    WorkloadName   string       `json:\"workloadName\"`\n    Namespace      string       `json:\"namespace\"`\n    Kind           string       `json:\"kind\"`\n    PodIP          string       `json:\"podIp,omitempty\"`\n    EntryPoints    []EntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints,omitempty\"`\n    CreatedAt      time.Time    `json:\"createdAt\"`\n    ExpiresAt      time.Time    `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n    Status         string       `json:\"status\"`\n    LastActivityAt time.Time    `json:\"lastActivityAt\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. VALKEY/REDIS CONFIGURATION\n\n### Environment Variables (from code):\n\n| Variable | Backend | Required | Default | Notes |\n|----------|---------|----------|---------|-------|\n| `STORE_TYPE` | Both | No | `redis` | Case-insensitive; `redis` or `valkey` |\n| `REDIS_ADDR` | Redis | Yes | -- | Single address |\n| `REDIS_PASSWORD` | Redis | Yes* | -- | Required unless `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` |\n| `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` | Redis | No | `true` | Case-insensitive `\"false\"` disables |\n| `VALKEY_ADDR` | Valkey | Yes | -- | Comma-separated addresses |\n| `VALKEY_PASSWORD` | Valkey | Yes* | -- | Required unless `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` |\n| `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` | Valkey | No | `true` | Case-insensitive `\"false\"` disables |\n| `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` | Valkey | No | `false` | `\"true\"` enables `DisableCache` |\n| `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` | Valkey | No | `false` | `\"true\"` enables `ForceSingleClient` |\n\n### No YAML/TOML config files exist for Valkey/Redis. All configuration is via environment variables.\n\n### Data Architecture (both backends):\n- String keys: `session:{sessionID}` -> JSON(SandboxInfo)\n- Sorted Set: `session:expiry` -> {sessionID: ExpiresAt.Unix()}\n- Sorted Set: `session:last_activity` -> {sessionID: lastActivity.Unix()}\n\n---\n\n## 6. AR-014 / ST-3 / ST-4 REFERENCES\n\n### AR-014 References:\nAR-014 is the **Valkey Storage Implementation** change request. Files directly related:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/proposal.md` -- 231-line proposal\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/design.md` -- 662-line detailed design\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-014/tasks.md` -- 109-line task checklist (5 task groups: T1-T5)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- 269-line delta spec for AR-014\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` -- SDD prompt referencing AR-014\n\n### ST-3 References:\nST-3 = \"Design Complete\" stage. Found in tasks.md headers:\n- AR-001/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-4 (Implementation)`\n- AR-002/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-004/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-005/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-006/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-007/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-008/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-4 (Implementation)`\n- AR-009/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-010/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-011/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-012/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-3 (Design Complete)`\n- AR-013/tasks.md: `Precondition: Stage ST-3 (Design) completed`\n- AR-014/tasks.md: `Precondition: Stage ST-3 (Design) completed`\n\n### ST-4 References:\nST-4 = \"Implementation\" stage. Found in:\n- AR-001/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-4 (Implementation)`\n- AR-008/tasks.md: `Stage: ST-4 (Implementation)`\n\n### Key observations about AR-014's current state:\n- The `tasks.md` shows **all tasks are unchecked** (no `[x]` markers), indicating implementation is not yet marked complete\n- The actual Go files (`store_valkey.go`, `store_valkey_test.go`) **DO exist** and contain full implementations\n- The Valkey implementation uses individual GET calls in List methods rather than MGET (the design doc describes MGET, but the code uses per-session `GetSandbox` calls)\n- The `design.md` at root level describes a slightly different Store interface (with `GetSandboxBySessionID` instead of `GetSandbox`, and different method signatures) than what is actually implemented in `store.go`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287ddd2bbffe6WAxRqmr0aqf5A","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775836998977,"end":1775837169531}}}}
